4780	These are the individual ingredients out of which \cref{lem:slice_dual_transport} and its
4781	inverse leg are assembled: the leg-(B) unit-ring swaps, their invertibility and cancellation
4782	identities, and the presheaf-level dual-of-unit identification. Each is a self-contained
4783	internal construction.
